<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1355359" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1961596102768_.pic_hd.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1125" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1961596102768_.pic_hd.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1961596102768_.pic_hd-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1961596102768_.pic_hd-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1961596102768_.pic_hd-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>α7S III ，索尼最新发布的全画幅微单， α7S 系列的最新款，一台专注于视频拍摄的相机。</p>
